BUSHBUCKRIDGE &#8211; On Saturday afternoon, three suspects shot a G4S Security guard four times in the legs when he had just collected cash from a shop at Twin City shopping centre.Despite his injuries, he kept running and returned fire at the suspects. This causing them to flee the scene without the cash.The men fled in a blue Citi Golf which was last seen heading in the direction of Graskop. The suspects are still at large.The guard was taken to Mediclinic Nelspruit where he is in a stable condition.Watch the video of the shooting here:&nbsp;&nbsp;